msgid "The benefits of up-to-date checks and the interaction of the build cache come with the cost of modeling the _inputs_ and _outputs_. Inputs are not only files or directories, but also the Java version used during the build, the operating system, the working directory, configuration options, and so on. So everything that influences the output of a task action must be declared as an input of the task."
